# Mortal Kombat Memory Card Game

## Overview

This is a fun and interactive memory card game based on the popular video game franchise, Mortal Kombat. The goal of the game is to click as many cards as you can without clicking the same card twice. This project was created as part of [The Odin Project JavaScript Curriculum track](https://www.theodinproject.com/paths/full-stack-javascript).

![Preview](preview.png)

Live preview of this project can be found [here](https://oche-memory-card.netlify.app/)

## How to Play

1. Click on a card to flip all the visible cards and reveal new ones.
2. The game is over when a card is clicke more than once.

## Installation

1. Clone this repository: `git clone https://github.com/EjembiEmmanuel/memory-card.git`
2. Navigate into the project directory: `cd memory-card`
3. Install the required dependencies: `npm install`
4. Start the game: `npm preview`

## Features

- Beautifully designed Mortal Kombat themed cards.
- Score tracker to keep track of your best score.
- Immersive background music and sound effects
- Responsive design that works on desktop, tablets, and phones.

